==Tree Gnome King==
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''King Bolren:''' Well hello stranger. My name's Bolren, I'm the king of the tree gnomes.
* '''King Bolren:''' I'm surprised you made it in, maybe I made the maze too easy.
* '''Player:''' Maybe.
* '''King Bolren:''' I'm afraid I have more serious concerns at the moment. Very serious.
* {{topt|Can I help at all?}}
** '''Player:''' Can I help at all?
** '''King Bolren:''' I'm glad you asked.
** '''King Bolren:''' The truth is my people are in grave danger. We have always been protected by the Spirit Tree. No creature of dark can harm us while its three orbs are in place.
** '''King Bolren:''' We are not a violent race, but we fight when we must. Many gnomes have fallen battling the dark forces of Khazard to the North.
** '''King Bolren:''' We became desperate, so we took one orb of protection to the battlefield. It was a foolish move.
** '''King Bolren:''' Khazard troops seized the orb. Now we are completely defenceless.
** '''Player:''' How can I help?
** '''King Bolren:''' You would be a huge benefit on the battlefield. If you would go there and try to retrieve the orb, my people and I will be forever grateful.
** {{tbox|Before starting this quest, be aware that your combat level is lower than the recommended level of 45.}}
** {{tselect|Start the Tree Gnome Village quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' I would be glad to help.
*** '''King Bolren:''' Thank you. The battlefield is to the north of the maze. Commander Montai will inform you of their current situation.
*** '''King Bolren:''' That is if he's still alive.
*** '''King Bolren:''' My assistant shall guide you out. Good luck friend, try your best to return the orb
*** {{tbox|Elkoy guides you out of the maze.}}
*** '''Elkoy:''' We're out of the maze now. Please hurry, we must have the orb if we are to survive.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm sorry but I won't be involved.
*** '''King Bolren:''' Ok then, travel safe.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I'll leave you to it then.}}
