** '''Commander Montai:''' Thank you, you're braver than most.
** '''Commander Montai:''' I don't know how long I will be able to hold out. Once you have the coordinates come back and fire the ballista right into those monsters.
** '''Commander Montai:''' If you can retrieve the orb and bring safety back to my people, none of the blood spilled on this field will be in vain.
** {{tact|end}}

